%% Data Flow Diagram for llama-stack-provider-ragas
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.3/llama-stack-provider-ragas.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as User / Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as RagasEvaluatorInline
    participant DatasetIO as DatasetIO API<br/>(in-process)
    participant Inference as Inference API<br/>(in-process)
    participant LLM as Ollama / vLLM<br/>11434/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 1: Inline Evaluation

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP/8321 plaintext
    LLS->>Inline: run_eval(benchmark_id, config)
    Inline->>DatasetIO: get_rows(dataset_id)
    DatasetIO-->>Inline: Dataset rows
    Inline->>Inference: LLM + Embeddings calls<br/>(via LlamaStackInlineLLM/Embeddings)
    Inference->>LLM: HTTP/11434 plaintext<br/>No auth
    LLM-->>Inference: Inference results
    Inference-->>Inline: LLM/Embedding responses
    Note over Inline: Run Ragas evaluate()<br/>(answer_relevancy, faithfulness,<br/>context_precision, context_recall)
    Inline-->>LLS: EvalResult
    LLS-->>Client: JSON Response

    participant Remote as RagasEvaluatorRemote
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod1 as KFP Pod: retrieve_data<br/>Container
    participant KFPPod2 as KFP Pod: run_ragas<br/>Container
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Remote Evaluation (Kubeflow Pipelines)

    Client->>LLS: POST /eval/run_eval<br/>HTTP/8321 plaintext
    LLS->>Remote: run_eval(benchmark_id, config)
    Remote->>KFP: Submit pipeline<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OAuth)
    KFP-->>Remote: Pipeline run ID
    Remote-->>LLS: Job ID (pending)
    LLS-->>Client: Job submitted

    KFP->>KFPPod1: Execute retrieve_data
    KFPPod1->>LLS: GET dataset rows<br/>HTTP/8321 plaintext
    LLS-->>KFPPod1: Dataset rows
    KFPPod1-->>KFP: Data artifact

    KFP->>KFPPod2: Execute run_ragas
    KFPPod2->>LLS: LLM + Embeddings calls<br/>HTTP/8321 plaintext<br/>(via LlamaStackRemoteLLM/Embeddings)
    LLS->>LLM: HTTP/11434 plaintext
    LLM-->>LLS: Inference results
    LLS-->>KFPPod2: Responses
    Note over KFPPod2: Run Ragas evaluate()
    KFPPod2->>S3: Store results (JSONL)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
    S3-->>KFPPod2: Upload confirmed

    Client->>LLS: GET /eval/job_result<br/>HTTP/8321
    LLS->>Remote: job_result(job_id)
    Remote->>S3: Fetch results<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    S3-->>Remote: JSONL results
    Remote-->>LLS: EvalResult
    LLS-->>Client: JSON Response
